---
// No props needed
---
<div class="my-12">
  <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-brand-navy mb-8 text-center">Pricing Overview</h2>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 max-w-5xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Card 1 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 flex flex-col hover:border-brand-sky transition-colors">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Rabbia Consultation</h3>
      <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-trust mb-4">
        USD 50 <span class="text-sm font-normal text-gray-500 block">/ AUD 75</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm flex-grow mb-6">Expert guidance with the Clinical Director for complex developmental concerns and strategic planning. Pakistan-based families may receive local pricing.</p>
      <a href="https://calendar.app.google/zMKejpnpCjh91WRG7" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="mt-auto w-full text-center bg-brand-navy text-white px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-blue-800 transition-colors">
        Book with Rabbia
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 2 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 flex flex-col hover:border-brand-sky transition-colors">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">Parent Guidance Session</h3>
      <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-trust mb-4">
        From USD 50
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm flex-grow mb-6">Standard consultation focusing on behavior, routines, and educational strategies with an associate provider.</p>
      <a href="/choose-a-provider" class="mt-auto w-full text-center bg-white text-brand-navy border border-brand-navy px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors">
        Choose a Provider
      </a>
    </div>

    <!-- Card 3 -->
    <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-sm border border-gray-200 p-6 flex flex-col hover:border-brand-sky transition-colors">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-brand-navy mb-2">School Consultation</h3>
      <div class="text-2xl font-bold text-brand-trust mb-4">
        From USD 75
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm flex-grow mb-6">Collaborative sessions involving parents, teachers, and school staff to align on support strategies.</p>
      <a href="/international-schools" class="mt-auto w-full text-center bg-brand-sky text-brand-navy px-4 py-2 rounded-lg font-medium hover:bg-blue-200 transition-colors">
        Learn More
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-4 max-w-5xl mx-auto mt-6">
    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center border border-gray-100">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy text-sm">Team Provider Consultation</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">Provider-specific rates</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center border border-gray-100">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy text-sm">Registered International Specialist</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">Provider-specific rates</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center border border-gray-100">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy text-sm">Digital Resources</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">Free to USD 29</p>
    </div>
    <div class="bg-gray-50 rounded-lg p-4 text-center border border-gray-100">
      <h4 class="font-semibold text-brand-navy text-sm">Workshops</h4>
      <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mt-1">USD 10–50</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto italic">
    Prices vary by provider, region, session type, and scope of service. Parents can review provider profiles and select the option that fits their needs before booking.
  </p>
</div>
